readable.content: A big dog and a smaller dog fight over a piece of fabric . A blonde dog is standing beside a blonde puppy , who is trying to get a stuffed animal from the adult dog . An adult golden retriever and a puppy are playing tug of war with a brown toy . An older dog and a younger one playing with a toy . The small , golden dog is attempting to take a furry object from a larger look-alike
